# System Prompt Configuration
# LOCAL DEVELOPMENT: Create a system_prompt.txt file (see system_prompt.example.txt for template)
# RAILWAY DEPLOYMENT: Set SYSTEM_PROMPT environment variable in Railway dashboard with your full prompt
