# The server will:
# 1. First try to load from system_prompt.txt (for local development)
# 2. Fall back to SYSTEM_PROMPT environment variable (for Railway)
#
# For Railway: Copy your entire system prompt and set it as SYSTEM_PROMPT env var in Railway dashboard
